<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    <div class="full-title with-title-branding">
      <div class="title-branding"><a href="/taxonomy/term/868"><img src="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/sites/bfi.org.uk/files/styles/16x9_small/public/sight-and-sound-logo-280x69.png?itok=AEegRSbk" alt="" /></a></div>
  
  <h1>
          Your world inside out: ¡Vivan las Antípodas! and Kossakovsky’s Ten Rules    
    
      </h1>

  
  
        <div class="copy">
              <div class="intro"><p>Victor Kossakovsky, documentary visionary, through his words and eyes.</p>
</div>
            
      
              <p class="author-data">
          <span class="author"><a href="/people/robert-greene"> Robert  Greene  </a></span><br /><span class="date">Updated: <time datetime="2019-07-24">24 July 2019</time></span>        </p>
      
      
          </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="block">
      
  <div class="content">
    
  <ul class="share">
          <li class="facebook_share"><div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/comment/unfiction/your-world-inside-out-vivan-las-antipodas" data-layout="standard"></div>
</li>
          <li class="field_tweetbutton"><div class="tweetbutton-tweet tweetbutton"><a href="http://twitter.com/share" data-size="medium" data-count="horizontal" data-via="SightSoundmag" data-related=":" data-text="Your world inside out: ¡Vivan las Antípodas! and Kossakovsky’s Ten Rules" data-counturl="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/comment/unfiction/your-world-inside-out-vivan-las-antipodas" data-url="https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/sight-sound-magazine/comment/unfiction/your-world-inside-out-vivan-las-antipodas" data-lang="" class="twitter-share-button">Tweet</a></div></li>
